}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== "A\N: GPCEB1040-000-PP402", "P\N:GEB1040 Rev.PP", "START: 2006/01/12", and model checkbox w/ options of '''GEB1040''' (checked) / '''GEH1040''' / '''GEB1045''' is silkscreened on one unit's board, as well as a date code of '''0617''' (Apr. 2006).
The Switch IC has a small / moderate size heatsink adhered to it. Radial caps on the board are largely '''Stone''' branded.
